Scotts buys remaining Miracle Garden stake . Scotts Co said it signed a letter of intent to buy the remaining 67 . 6 percent interest in Britain ' s Miracle Garden Care Ltd that it does not own for an undisclosed amount . The acquisition , expected to be completed in January , will have " netural to slightly accretive earnings implications for Scotts in 1997 , " the company said in a statement . The company provided no further details and could not be immediately reached to comment . The acquisition will help the company expand in Europe ' s lawn care and garden products market , Scotts said . 
